(1, 1, '2016-09-08 08:44:22', '2016-09-08 08:44:22', 'Pragmatic Linux is a Linux distribution based on Arch Linux which offers all capabilities for Web Development and an already setup Server Environment. Pragmatic Linux is fast and lightweight while still acting as a stable Operating System. It comes as a 64-bit version and has many different built-in tools. It is licensed and protected by various license communities. Pragmatic Linux is also available as a standalone Web Server version.\r\n<div class="text-center">\r\n<a href="/downloads" class="btn btn-primary">Get Pragmatic Linux</a>\r\n</div>', 'What is Pragmatic Linux?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'what-is-pragmatic-linux', '', '', '2016-09-16 22:42:14', '2016-09-16 22:42:14', '', 0, 'http://dev.pragmaticlinux:8080/?p=1', 0, 'post', '', 1),
