(115, 1, '2016-09-16 20:26:51', '2016-09-16 20:26:51', '<div class="col-md-12">\n<pre>The following Pragmatic Linux logos are available for press and other use.</pre>\n<h3>Two-color standard version</h3>\nAvailable on <a href="http://pragmaticlinux.org/AlbanMulaki/PragmaticLinux/logo/PragramaticLinuxLogoInvert.png" target="_blank">PNG</a>.\n\n<a href="http://pragmaticlinux.org/AlbanMulaki/PragmaticLinux/logo/PragramaticLinuxLogo.png"><img class="img-responsive" src="http://pragmaticlinux.org/AlbanMulaki/PragmaticLinux/logo/PragramaticLinuxLogo.png" alt="" width="1114" height="260" /></a>\n\n<hr />\n\n<h3><strong>Two-color  inverted version</strong></h3>\n<a href="http://pragmaticlinux.org/AlbanMulaki/PragmaticLinux/logo/PragramaticLinuxLogoInvert.png"><img class="img-responsive" src="http://pragmaticlinux.org/AlbanMulaki/PragmaticLinux/logo/PragramaticLinuxLogoInvert.png" alt="" width="1114" height="260" /></a>\n\nAvailable on <a href="http://pragmaticlinux.org/AlbanMulaki/PragmaticLinux/logo/PragramaticLinuxLogoInvert.png" target="_blank">PNG</a>.\n\n<hr />\n\n<h3><strong>Two-Color Icon Pragmatic Logo</strong></h3>\n<a href="http://pragmaticlinux.org/AlbanMulaki/PragmaticLinux/logo/PragmaticLinuxIcon.png"><img class="img-responsive" src="http://pragmaticlinux.org/AlbanMulaki/PragmaticLinux/logo/PragmaticLinuxIcon.png" alt="" width="230" height="241" /></a>\n\nAvailable on <a href="http://pragmaticlinux.org/AlbanMulaki/PragmaticLinux/logo/PragmaticLinuxIcon.png">PNG</a>.\n\n<hr />\n\n&nbsp;\n<h5>Banner Standard</h5>\n<a href="http://pragmaticlinux.org/AlbanMulaki/PragmaticLinux/background/PragmaticLinuxBlueBanner.jpg"><img class="img-responsive" src="http://pragmaticlinux.org/AlbanMulaki/PragmaticLinux/background/PragmaticLinuxBlueBanner.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="187" /></a>\n\nAvailable on <a href="http://pragmaticlinux.org/AlbanMulaki/PragmaticLinux/background/PragmaticLinuxBlueBanner.jpg">PNG</a>.\n\n<hr />\n\n&nbsp;\n<h3>Banner Inverted</h3>\n<a href="http://pragmaticlinux.org/AlbanMulaki/PragmaticLinux/background/PragmaticLinuxWhiteBanner.jpg"><img class="img-responsive" src="http://pragmaticlinux.org/AlbanMulaki/PragmaticLinux/background/PragmaticLinuxWhiteBanner.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="187" /></a>\n\nAvailable on <a href="http://pragmaticlinux.org/AlbanMulaki/PragmaticLinux/background/PragmaticLinuxWhiteBanner.jpg">PNG</a>.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<hr />\n\n&nbsp;\n<h3></h3>\n<h3>Background</h3>\nPragmatic Linux v0.6\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<img class="img-responsive" src="http://pragmaticlinux.org/AlbanMulaki/PragmaticLinux/background/PragmaticLinuxBlueWD.jpg" alt="" width="2400" height="1445" />\n\n&nbsp;\n\nAvailable on Widescreen <a href="http://pragmaticlinux.org/AlbanMulaki/PragmaticLinux/background/PragmaticLinuxBlueWD.jpg">PNG</a> and 4:3 <a href="http://pragmaticlinux.org/AlbanMulaki/PragmaticLinux/background/PragmaticLinuxBlueWD.jp">PNG</a>.\n\n<hr />\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<img class="img-responsive" src="http://pragmaticlinux.org/AlbanMulaki/PragmaticLinux/background/PragmaticLinuxWD.jpg" alt="" width="2400" height="1445" />\n\nAvailable on Widescreen <a href="http://pragmaticlinux.org/AlbanMulaki/PragmaticLinux/background/PragmaticLinuxWD.jpg">PNG</a> and 4:3 <a href="http://pragmaticlinux.org/AlbanMulaki/PragmaticLinux/background/PragmaticLinux.jpg">PNG</a>.\n\n<hr />\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<img class="img-responsive" src="http://pragmaticlinux.org/AlbanMulaki/PragmaticLinux/background/PragmaticLinuxWhiteWD.jpg" alt="" width="2400" height="1445" />\n\nAvailable on Widescreen <a href="http://pragmaticlinux.org/AlbanMulaki/PragmaticLinux/background/PragmaticLinuxWhiteWD.jpg">PNG </a>and 4:3 <a href="http://pragmaticlinux.org/AlbanMulaki/PragmaticLinux/background/PragmaticLinuxWhite.jpg">PNG</a>.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<hr />\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n<h3>Pragmatic Linux Old Wallpaper</h3>\n<img class="img-responsive" src="http://pragmaticlinux.org/AlbanMulaki/PragmaticLinux/background/PragmaticLnuxOld.jpg" alt="" width="1600" height="952" />\n\nAvailable on Widescreen <a href="http://pragmaticlinux.org/AlbanMulaki/PragmaticLinux/background/PragmaticLnuxOld.jpg">PNG</a>.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n</div>', 'Pragmatic Linux Logos and Artwork', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '91-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-09-16 20:26:51', '2016-09-16 20:26:51', '', 91, 'http://dev.pragmaticlinux:8080/91-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
