(124, 1, '2014-12-22 20:32:14', '2014-12-22 20:32:14', 'New distro of linux is coming, it will bring new feature and environment.\r\n\r\nPragmaticLinux is userfriendly Linux distribution based on indepedently <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arch_Linux">Arch Linux OS</a>. ArchLinux is developed to be fast,powerful, lightweight thats provide access to the very latest cutting edge and bleeding edge - software. Arch aimed at more experienced or technically-minded user. PragmaticLinux developed on Kosova provides all the benefits of ArchLinux combined with a focus on fast development software and environment. Available only on 64-Bit Archictecture. PragmaticLinux is suitable for developer, students learning on programming, as well as experienced developer and linux user.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Pragmatic Linux offers :</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>New Environment and fast</li>\r\n 	<li>Development Tools</li>\r\n 	<li>Learning Tools</li>\r\n 	<li>OWASP</li>\r\n 	<li>Frameworks</li>\r\n 	<li>Stress Testing</li>\r\n 	<li>Guide</li>\r\n 	<li>Programming Tutorials</li>\r\n 	<li>Most Usable programming forum</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nFor more experienced, adventurous users PragmaticLinux also offers the the configurabilty and versatility to be shaped and modules in every aspect of personale taste,preferences,performance tunning. Furthermore we will provide minimalistic edition starting from a command line, be completely free to chose your own greeters, desktops, hardware drivers, software applications, and so on\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>History</h2>\r\nPragmatic Linux was founded by Alban Mulaki. PragmaticLinux is based on Arch Linux, inspired by inspired by needs of software and web development.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2 id="functionality">Functionality</h2>\r\nPragmatic Linux brings lot of tools and accessories for you, without losing performance with those kind of environment pragmatic linux still lightweight and fast.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2 id="environment">Environment</h2>\r\nDefault desktop is XFCE. which doesnt require good graphic card and hight performance its easy and lightweight desktop.\r\n<div>\r\n<table style="height: 45px;" border="1" width="185" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Required RAM</td>\r\n<td>192 MB</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Required CPU</td>\r\n<td>300 MHz</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nThis is Alpha Version Desktop of pragmatic linux.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://pragmatic/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/s1.png"><img class="alignnone wp-image-167" src="http://pragmatic/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/s1.png" alt="s1" width="761" height="457" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2 id="advantages">Advantages</h2>\r\nPragmatic linux have heavy advantages over other linux distro, and other OS like(Windows, MAC).\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Freedom</li>\r\n 	<li>Very stable</li>\r\n 	<li>Less vulnerable by windows malware and viruses</li>\r\n 	<li>Pragmatic Linux typically does not slow down over time</li>\r\n 	<li>Can run on old computers</li>\r\n 	<li>The choices its on your hand with linux</li>\r\n 	<li>Open-Source</li>\r\n 	<li>Performance</li>\r\n 	<li>Flexibility</li>\r\n 	<li>Compatibility</li>\r\n 	<li>Free</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>Summary</h2>\r\nTo summarize: Pragmatic Linux is design for web developer, software developer and new comer on programming.It is powerful and easy to manage, making it an ideal distro for programmers and those who want to be.', 'Pragmatic Linux Distribution for Web Developer', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'pragmatic-linux-distribution-for-web-developer', '', '', '2016-09-16 20:34:39', '2016-09-16 20:34:39', '', 0, 'http://dev.pragmaticlinux:8080/?p=124', 0, 'post', '', 0),
