(132, 1, '2015-06-14 20:15:20', '2015-06-14 20:15:20', 'We are happy you announc you that 16-June-2015 the first alpha version will be released as Virtual Disk where you can test it on virtualbox or vmware, its not stable version. As soon we find some donor and sponsor the project will be boost up fast.\r\n\r\nPragmaticLinux Alpha Version 0.4v\r\nThere are some of part almost done and where we are working on, you can contribute on this project just by report bugs on <a href="http://www.pragmaticlinux.org/bugs/" target="_blank">www.pragmaticlinux.org/bugs/</a> this kind of help will be really helpful.\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong><span style="color: #339966;">Ready environment with tools</span></strong></li>\r\n<li><strong><span style="color: #339966;">Web Development</span></strong></li>\r\n<li><strong><span style="color: #339966;">Frameworks</span></strong></li>\r\n<li><strong><span style="color: #339966;">Fast environment and lightweight</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThe image tested just on <strong>VirtualBox</strong> and <strong>VMWare</strong>.\r\n\r\n<strong>Minimum Requirements:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Memory</strong>: 500MB</li>\r\n<li><strong>CPU</strong>:  Pentium 4 or higher</li>\r\n<li><strong>GPU</strong>: Works on anyone</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe need <strong>sponsor</strong> for this project to boost up the idea and develop it faster. if anyone is interested can contact on <a href="mailto:donate@pragmaticlinux.org">donate@pragmaticlinux.org</a>\r\n\r\nThank you for supporting us.\r\n\r\nPragmatic Linux', 'Pragmatic Linux First Releases VirtualDisk - Alpha 0.4v', 'Pragmatic Linux First Release in VirtualDisk Mode - Alpha 0.4v, Frameworks, Web Development, Environment, Pre-configured server.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'pragmatic-linux-first-releases-virtualdisk-alpha-0-4v', '', '', '2016-09-16 20:40:50', '2016-09-16 20:40:50', '', 0, 'http://dev.pragmaticlinux:8080/?p=132', 0, 'post', '', 0),
