(137, 1, '2016-05-13 17:47:08', '2016-05-13 17:47:08', 'We pronounce that soon we will release the new edition of pragmatic linux Called "Pragmatic Linux Env" - it can be used as Web Server which offer it with configurated environment for work and development.\r\n\r\nSome feature services that are inside of Pragmatic Linux Env:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Apache</li>\r\n	<li>MySQL</li>\r\n	<li>PHP</li>\r\n	<li>FTP</li>\r\n	<li>SSH</li>\r\n	<li>SMB Share</li>\r\n	<li>Webmin Administration Panel - Web Interface</li>\r\n	<li>phpmyadmin</li>\r\n	<li>Port Forwarding customize</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nFirst release will be on May 2016, for more accurated date stay in  touch with us.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Pragmatic Linux Env v1.0 - Web Server', 'Release Pragmatic Linux Server 1.0v Many Features, Apache, MySQL, PHP, FTP, DNS, SSH, SMB Share, Webmin, phpmyadmin, PortForwarding, VirtualMachine Instance', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'pragmatic-linux-env-v1-0-web-server', '', '', '2016-09-16 20:46:15', '2016-09-16 20:46:15', '', 0, 'http://dev.pragmaticlinux:8080/?p=137', 0, 'post', '', 0);
