(140, 1, '2016-09-16 20:46:15', '2016-09-16 20:46:15', 'We pronounce that soon we will release the new edition of pragmatic linux Called "Pragmatic Linux Env" - it can be used as Web Server which offer it with configurated environment for work and development.\r\n\r\nSome feature services that are inside of Pragmatic Linux Env:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Apache</li>\r\n	<li>MySQL</li>\r\n	<li>PHP</li>\r\n	<li>FTP</li>\r\n	<li>SSH</li>\r\n	<li>SMB Share</li>\r\n	<li>Webmin Administration Panel - Web Interface</li>\r\n	<li>phpmyadmin</li>\r\n	<li>Port Forwarding customize</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nFirst release will be on May 2016, for more accurated date stay in  touch with us.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Pragmatic Linux Env v1.0 - Web Server', 'Release Pragmatic Linux Server 1.0v Many Features, Apache, MySQL, PHP, FTP, DNS, SSH, SMB Share, Webmin, phpmyadmin, PortForwarding, VirtualMachine Instance', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '137-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-09-16 20:46:15', '2016-09-16 20:46:15', '', 137, 'http://dev.pragmaticlinux:8080/137-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(141, 1, '2016-07-18 14:20:10', '2016-07-18 14:20:10', 'We are delighted to announce that the new version of <strong>Pragmatic Linux</strong> is now available for download.\r\nThis version comes with a lot of new features. The biggest feature is the new <em>installation</em> process which enables a faster and easier way for installing of Pragmatic Linux.\r\nAnother big feature is that Pragmatic Linux now includes <strong>Pragmatic-dev software</strong> for managing services and projects.\r\nA lot of new services have been integrated. Also this version is more <em>stable</em> and <em>usable</em>.\r\n\r\nDownload <a href="http://www.pragmaticlinux.org/downloads-pragmatic/" target="_blank">here</a>.', 'Pragmatic Linux 0.6v Available for download', 'Pragmatic Linux 0.6v, Features Installation, bootable,  software called pragmatic-dev, services improvment, stability.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'pragmatic-linux-0-6v-available-for-download', '', '', '2016-09-16 20:49:22', '2016-09-16 20:49:22', '', 0, 'http://dev.pragmaticlinux:8080/?p=141', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(142, 1, '2016-09-16 20:49:10', '2016-09-16 20:49:10', 'We are delighted to announce that the new version of <strong>Pragmatic Linux</strong> is now available for download.\r\nThis version comes with a lot of new features. The biggest feature is the new <em>installation</em> process which enables a faster and easier way for installing of Pragmatic Linux.\r\nAnother big feature is that Pragmatic Linux now includes <strong>Pragmatic-dev software</strong> for managing services and projects.\r\nA lot of new services have been integrated. Also this version is more <em>stable</em> and <em>usable</em>.\r\n\r\nDownload <a href="http://www.pragmaticlinux.org/downloads-pragmatic/" target="_blank">here</a>.', 'Pragmatic Linux 0.6v Available for download', 'Pragmatic Linux 0.6v, Features Installation, bootable,  software called pragmatic-dev, services improvment, stability.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '141-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-09-16 20:49:10', '2016-09-16 20:49:10', '', 141, 'http://dev.pragmaticlinux:8080/141-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
