(155, 1, '2016-09-16 22:27:53', '2016-09-16 22:27:53', 'Pragmatic Linux is a Linux distribution based on Arch Linux which offers all capabilities for Web Development and an already setup Server Environment. Pragmatic Linux is fast and lightweight while still acting as a stable Operating System. It comes as a 64-bit version and has many different built-in tools. It is licensed and protected by various license communities. Pragmatic Linux is also available as a standalone Web Server version.\r\n\r\n<a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">DOWNLOAD</a>', 'What is Pragmatic Linux?', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-09-16 22:27:53', '2016-09-16 22:27:53', '', 1, 'http://dev.pragmaticlinux:8080/1-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
