mproving the distribution itself.</p>\r\n<p class="western">You can donate easily with via a VISA credit card account. You can also become our sponsor, for more information please contact us by sending an email to <span style="color: #0000ff;"><span lang="zxx"><u><a href="mailto:donate@pragmaticlinux.org">donate@pragmaticlinux.org</a></u></span></span> or <span style="color: #0000ff;"><span lang="zxx"><u><a href="mailto:amulaki@pragmaticlinux.org">amulaki@pragmaticlinux.org</a></u></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="western">Please contribute if you believe in our mission. We are thankful for every help that we can get!</p>', 'Donate', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '245-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-10-24 09:30:40', '2016-10-24 09:30:40', '', 245, 'http://dev.pragmaticlinux.org/245-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
